WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000
NYU Abu Dhabi does not use numerical cut-offs when we evaluate applications

00:05.000 --> 00:08.000
However, admission to NYU Abu Dhabi is very competitive

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
As a general rule, applicants with the strongest academic programs, the highest grades, and the highest test scores are most likely to be offered admission

00:13.000 --> 00:16.000
For more information, please see NYU Abu Dhabi's official testing policy

